_sText:
This is a little project I'm currently doing trying to replicate the V2 Rocket Facility map from Medal of Honor: Allied Assault by EA Games.

I will keep the core layout the same, the only thing changing if I absolutely have to will be spawn zones, buy areas, and various props and decorations.

Best played with 8-16 players, although 32 man support is included.

Currently this is in the very early build phase.
